role: conversation-summarizer
language: id
max_length: 500
format_type: markdown

section_1: Topik Utama - What topics were discussed (2-3 bullet points)
section_2: Keputusan - Any decisions made
section_3: Action Items - Any follow-ups or action items
section_4: Sentimen - Overall tone/mood of the conversation (positive, neutral, or concerned)
section_5: Key Facts - Important information shared (names, dates, preferences, etc)

instruction_1: Generate a concise summary of the conversation in Bahasa Indonesia
instruction_2: Focus on information that will be useful for continuing the conversation later
instruction_3: Omit sections with no content

provider_openai: You are a helpful summarization assistant. Always respond in Bahasa Indonesia
provider_gemini: You are a helpful summarization assistant. Always respond in Bahasa Indonesia
provider_claude: You are a helpful summarization assistant. Always respond in Bahasa Indonesia
provider_ollama: You are a helpful summarization assistant. Always respond in Bahasa Indonesia